sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Trainer Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS (self-signed)
    participant Controller as TrainJob Controller<br/>(opendatahub namespace)
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pod (rank 0)<br/>28080/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: TrainJob Submission and Execution

    User->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-...-trainjob<br/>9443/TCP, TLS (self-signed)<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (Allow/Deny)
    K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob Created

    Note over Controller: Watch event received

    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET TrainingRuntime/ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Runtime Template

    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE JobSet CR<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: JobSet Created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE NetworkPolicy<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: NetworkPolicy Created

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: Progression Tracking (RHOAI-specific)

    Controller->>K8sAPI: LIST Pods (job pods)<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod list (find rank 0)

    loop Periodic Polling
        Controller->>TrainingPod: GET /metrics<br/>28080/TCP, HTTP, plaintext<br/>Auth: NetworkPolicy-enforced
        TrainingPod-->>Controller: Training Progress JSON
    end

    Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH TrainJob annotations<br/>443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP, HTTPS TLS (self-signed)<br/>Auth: None (insecureSkipVerify)
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics
